nodes.text: Mission to the twelfth moon of Yout

Some time before the Battle of Teth, the assassin droid KRONOS-327 was sent on a mission to the twelfth moon of Yout by Ziro the Hutt, to assassinate someone. The mission ended in his failure. KRONOS-327 returned to Ziro's Palace on Coruscant to report his failure. Ziro was displeased with KRONOS-327's failure, and ordered he be turned into spare parts.
